title: FF C. M. Hughes - This Time She Had Gone Too Far
description:
Publication Date: June 8, 2013

A lighthearted and risque tale centred around two women living in a small Welsh village in the 1910's. When owner of Cristal House, Cissy Boye, employs the beautiful Fanny Greene to care for her barmy mother a torrid love affair ensues. Containing humour and tragedy with a number of entertaining characters, this book shows where their relationship leads them.
